
<span class='GTTabs_titles'><b>Translation</b></span><br />
I would like, I would like<br />
To stay with you looking into the sun<br />
I would pray, I would pray<br />
To see the rainbow</p>
<p>And so if another day dies<br />
I would search in your eyes<br />
To find those words<br />
Saying I love you, I love you, I love you</p>
<p>I would like, I would like<br />
To hold your hands in mine<br />
Even if there will never be<br />
A star of my love in the sky</p>
